com.test.automation.common.framework

Class XMLToMapParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • com.test.automation.common.framework.XMLToMapParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataToMapParser, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler

    public class XMLToMapParser
extends DefaultHandler
implements DataToMapParser
    Simple SAX parser that maps an XML file to a map of maps. Attributes are simply rolled in as key value pairs on the given node that they come in on. For repeated node names, a list is created. The order is maintained as parsed. Everything parsed is treated as simple text, there is no attempt to validate.
    Author:
    SaiGnapika
